data.description: This just feels like home! Bright and cheery foyer welcomes you. Features include new dual HVAC units, fixtures, built in surround sound, storm shelter. This home also has open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, efficient kitchen with center island and all appliances. Storage galore with attic & oversized closets in every room. Enjoy your evenings entertaining outdoors with shaded patio, HUGE privacy fenced back yard or take your family for a walk on the Frisco Trail.
